Entire word search rewritten: Now the search is done as usual, then before returning the result it is checked to be a
whole word, if not, the next result is searched (and checked).<br/>

A whole word has the following conditions:<br/><br/>

start of word :  
<ul>
	<li>beginning of the line</li>
	<li>starts with a symbol or space</li>
	<li>char before the first char is a symbol or space</li>
</ul>
	
end of word:
<ul>
	<li>end of line</li>
	<li>ends with a symbol or space</li>
	<li>char next to the last char is a symbol or space</li>
</ul>
	
